                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>A large stone krater, or vase, with simple pedestal foot, rim, and two handles. Judged by Ferrua to be a compact local limestone, rather than a marble. The text is heavily worn and not entirely legible</p>
                                    <material ana="" type="stone.limestone" subtype="unverified" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html">limestone</material>
